						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up near the steps leading to the south <hi rend="italic">prākāra</hi> of Śāntīśvara-basti.</p>						

						<p>1484-85 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record seems to register a gift to the Kannaḍi-basti probably by Nārasiṁha-banga.</p>						

						<p>It is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1406</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1484-85 A.D.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
